ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Swan River Chamber of Commerce CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval to grant the application of the SWAN RIVER CHAMBER OF COMMERCE in Manitoba (a) to change its name to the SWAN VALLEY CHAMBER OF COMMERCE and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to correspond to the perimeter of G-7 including Pine River and Cowan. G-7 boundaries are: to the North – 11 kilometres North of Mafeking; to the South - rural municipality of Swan River boundary; to the West – Saskatchewan Border and to the East – Pine River.
